---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="810 West 7th Street">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8 text-center">810 West 7th Street</h1>

    <!-- Property Image Gallery -->
    <div class="grid gap-4 grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 mb-10">
      {[
        "IMG_6447.JPEG",
        "IMG_6448.JPEG",
        "IMG_6449.JPEG",
        "IMG_6450.JPEG",
        "IMG_6451.JPEG",
        "IMG_6452.JPEG",
        "IMG_6453.JPEG",
        "IMG_6454.JPEG",
        "IMG_6455.JPEG",
        "IMG_6456.JPEG",
        "IMG_6457.JPEG",
        "IMG_6458.JPEG",
        "IMG_6459.JPEG",
        "IMG_6460.JPEG",
        "IMG_6461.JPEG",
        "IMG_6463.JPEG",
      ].map((filename) => (
        <a href={`https://sentinel-power-blog-resources.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/Properties/${filename}`} data-lightbox="gallery">
          <img
            src={`https://sentinel-power-blog-resources.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/Properties/${filename}`}
            alt="Property image"
            class="rounded-lg shadow-md object-cover w-full h-64 hover:opacity-90 transition"
          />
        </a>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- Property Highlights Section -->
    <section class="mt-12 space-y-8">
      <!-- Overview -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Property Overview</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-400">
          810 W 7th Street is a recently renovated 2,000 sq ft commercial building in a
          prime stretch of Sioux City’s revitalized West 7th corridor . Built in 1987, this
          standalone structure features updated roofing, façade, and two newly renovated bathrooms.
          Whether you're launching a boutique retail store, professional office, or service
          business, this property offers a versatile, move-in ready space with strong street
          presence thanks to the remodeled drive-through window .
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Key Features -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Key Features</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-zinc-400 space-y-2">
          <li>2,000 sq ft interior space on a 0.09‑acre lot</li>
          <li>Two updated restrooms for staff and clients</li>
          <li>Drive-through window, ideal for service-based businesses</li>
          <li>New flooring, façade, plumbing, roof, and framing</li>
          <li>Commercial C zoning — flexible for retail, office, or service</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Location Perks -->
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4">Location Highlights</h2>
        <p class="text-zinc-400 space-y-4">
          Located in the heart of Sioux City’s West 7th Corridor, a historically rich commercial district undergoing revitalization.<br>
          Easy access to highways, downtown, local schools, and a solid customer base (16,000+ within a mile, median income ~$41k).<br>
          The street has been recently upgraded with widened lanes, extra parking, and improved streetscape for pedestrian appeal. <br>
          <br>

          If you want more information or want to schedule a visit, please contact this number: 712-301-0871
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
